  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You&rsquo;ve always been fascinated with the ancient race of sphinxes, and are inspired by them to love puzzles and riddles and enjoy solving difficult dilemmas. Like so many others, you&rsquo;ve come to Wati to explore its ancient necropolis, but you&rsquo;ve also heard that sphinxes occasionally visit a sphinx-shaped ruin called Ubet&rsquo;s Folly in the city&mdash;perhaps you&rsquo;ll have the chance to meet and talk with a sphinx yourself!</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You gain a +1 trait bonus on Bluff and Diplomacy checks against sphinxes, and a +1 trait bonus on any skill check to decipher a puzzle or riddle. In addition, you may choose Sphinx as one of your bonus languages.</span></p>",
